Class MutableHandlerRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.grpc.HandlerRegistry
      • io.grpc.MutableHandlerRegistry
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MutableHandlerRegistryImpl

    @ThreadSafe
 @ExperimentalApi(value="https://github.com/grpc/grpc-java/issues/933")
public abstract class MutableHandlerRegistry
extends HandlerRegistry
    Mutable base class of HandlerRegistry. Used by server implementations that need to bind and unbind services that are exposed to remote clients.
